9/12 Lecture notes

Project Management

Initiation -> Planning and design -> Execution -> testing/monitor/control -> Closing
                     ^---------------------------------------v

Project management tools:
Team contract, timeline, mission statements, project status reports, action item list (every week), meetings
Gantt chart - put dates like snapshot on the calendar/to do list
Leave room for error
Check out schedule templates on uidaho mindworks

Budget - This does not apply to us
Shop resources - Also does not apply to us


